pokedexEntries.red: A rare and elusive Pokémon that is said to bring happiness to those who manage to get it.
pokedexEntries.blue: A rare and elusive Pokémon that is said to bring happiness to those who manage to get it.
pokedexEntries.yellow: A gentle and kind-hearted Pokémon that shares its nutritious eggs if it sees an injured Pokémon.
pokedexEntries.gold: It walks carefully to prevent its egg from breaking. However, it is extremely fast at running away.
pokedexEntries.silver: Few in numbers and difficult to capture, it is said to bring happiness to the trainer who catches it.
pokedexEntries.crystal: People try to catch it for its extremely nutritious eggs, but it rarely can be found.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Chansey lays nutritionally excellent eggs on an everyday basis. The eggs are so delicious, they are easily and eagerly devoured by even those people who have lost their appetite.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Chansey lays nutritionally excellent eggs on an everyday basis. The eggs are so delicious, they are easily and eagerly devoured by even those people who have lost their appetite.
pokedexEntries.emerald: Chansey lay nutritionally excellent eggs every day. The eggs are so delicious, they are eagerly devoured by even those people who have lost their appetite.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It lays several eggs a day. The eggs are apparently rich in nutrients and extremely delicious.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: A rare and elusive Pokémon that is said to bring happiness to those who manage to get it.
pokedexEntries.diamond: It is said to deliver happiness. Being compassionate, it shares its eggs with injured people.
pokedexEntries.pearl: It lays several eggs a day and won't share them with those who have evil in their hearts.
pokedexEntries.platinum: A kindly Pokémon that lays highly nutritious eggs and shares them with injured Pokémon or people.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: It walks carefully to prevent its egg from breaking. However, it is extremely fast at running away.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: Being few in number and difficult to capture, it is said to bring happiness to the Trainer who catches it.
pokedexEntries.black: A kindly Pokémon that lays highly nutritious eggs and shares them with injured Pokémon or people.
pokedexEntries.white: A kindly Pokémon that lays highly nutritious eggs and shares them with injured Pokémon or people.

pokedexEntries.white2: A kindly Pokémon that lays highly nutritious eggs and shares them with injured Pokémon or people.
pokedexEntries.x: It is said to deliver happiness. Being compassionate, it shares its eggs with injured people.
pokedexEntries.y: It lays several eggs a day. The eggs are apparently rich in nutrients and extremely delicious.
pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: Chansey lays nutritionally excellent eggs on an everyday basis. The eggs are so delicious, they are easily and eagerly devoured by even those people who have lost their appetite.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: Chansey lays nutritionally excellent eggs on an everyday basis. The eggs are so delicious, they are easily and eagerly devoured by even those people who have lost their appetite.
pokedexEntries.sun: The eggs laid by Chansey are rich in nutrients and a favorite food of many Pokémon.
pokedexEntries.moon: Not only are these Pokémon fast runners, they're also few in number, so anyone who finds one must be lucky indeed.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: It seems that other Pokémon’s efforts to take its delicious, nutritious egg away from it caused Chansey to get faster at fleeing.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: Because the eggs on their bellies have been overharvested by people in the past, the Chansey population remains very small.
